@startuml
' Diagram: F02 - Tai va kham pha danh sach POI (Sequence)
' Status: VERIFIED
' Baseline: branch master, current worktree @ HEAD 8ed8643
' Source:
' - VinhKhanhTourDemo/MainPage.xaml.cs: OnAppearing(), LoadPoisFromApi(), RestoreSubscriptionStateAsync(), RestorePoiHistoryAsync(), RefreshMapIfNeeded(), LoadMap(), GetMapPoiSignature(), GetPoiVisualPositions(), ShowMapPoiSheet(), OnSearchTextChanged(), OpenPoiDetailAsync(), RecordPoiViewAsync(), SyncPoiHistoryAsync(), RefreshPoisInBackgroundAsync(), UpdateCaiDatUI(), OnCopyDeviceCodeClicked(), OnPasteDeviceCodeClicked(), OnScanDeviceQrClicked(), OnRestoreDeviceCodeClicked(), RestoreDeviceCodeAsync()
' - VinhKhanhTourDemo/QrScannerPage.xaml.cs: OnBarcodesDetected()
' - VinhKhanhTourDemo/DeviceIdentity.cs: GetDeviceId(), BuildRecoveryPayload(), BuildQrCodeUrl(), TrySetDeviceIdOverride()
' - VinhKhanhTour.API/Controllers/PoiController.cs: GetAll()
' - VinhKhanhTour.API/Controllers/HeartbeatController.cs: GetExperienceProfile(), RecordView(), SyncHistory()
' - VinhKhanhTour.API/Controllers/SubscriptionController.cs: GetStatus()
' Note: Sequence chi tiet hoa fallback data, restore profile/XP, map sheet, viewed history, va luong khoi phuc ma thiet bi trong MainPage.
' Note: Map dung geofence circle theo toa do that cua POI, co the render marker offset de de nhin, va chi rebuild HTML map khi GetMapPoiSignature() thay doi.
' Note: Luong ghi nhan "visit" khi geofence trigger (POST /api/heartbeat/visit) duoc mo hinh rieng trong F03 (Geofence/Audio) de tach concern.
' Note: Tu v1.5.2, ConLaiNgay trong /api/heartbeat/profile va SoNgayConLai trong /api/subscription/status deu tinh bang Math.Floor((NgayHetHan - now).TotalDays) min 0. Helper SubscriptionState.CalculateRemainingDays dung chung trong app.
title F02 - Tai va kham pha danh sach POI

actor Guest
participant MainPage
participant DeviceIdentity
participant Clipboard
participant QrScannerPage
participant AppConfig
participant "PoiController" as PoiController
participant "HeartbeatController" as HeartbeatController
participant "SubscriptionController" as SubscriptionController
participant Preferences
participant "Leaflet WebView" as MapWebView
participant DetailPage
database DB

Guest -> MainPage: mo man Explore
MainPage -> MainPage: OnAppearing()\nApplyLocalizedUiText()\nUpdateCaiDatUI()
MainPage -> DeviceIdentity: BuildRecoveryPayload()
DeviceIdentity --> MainPage: payload
MainPage -> DeviceIdentity: BuildQrCodeUrl()
DeviceIdentity --> MainPage: qrUrl
MainPage -> AppConfig: EnsureApiBaseUrlAsync()
MainPage -> PoiController: GET /api/poi
alt API tra du lieu thanh cong
  PoiController -> DB: query POI dang hoat dong\nNgayHetHanDuyTri >= now
  DB --> PoiController: danh sach POI
  PoiController --> MainPage: List<PoiDto>
  MainPage -> MainPage: _isUsingFallbackData = false\n_lastDataLoadError = null
else API loi / khong reachable
  PoiController --> MainPage: exception
  MainPage -> MainPage: CreateFallbackPois()\n_isUsingFallbackData = true\n_lastDataLoadError = ex.Message
end
MainPage -> MainPage: RefreshMapIfNeeded()
alt MapWebView chua tao hoac POI signature thay doi
  MainPage -> MainPage: LoadMap()\nGetPoiVisualPositions()
  MainPage -> MapWebView: render geofence circles o true lat/lng\nrender markers o display lat/lng
  MapWebView --> MainPage: map html loaded
else map da ton tai va signature giong nhau
  MainPage -> MapWebView: updateUserLocation()/highlightPoi() neu can
end
MainPage -> MainPage: RenderPoiCards()\nUpdateApiConnectionUi()

opt restore lich su/XP tu server
  MainPage -> DeviceIdentity: GetDeviceId()
  MainPage -> AppConfig: EnsureApiBaseUrlAsync()
  MainPage -> HeartbeatController: GET /api/heartbeat/profile/{maThietBi}
  HeartbeatController -> DB: doc LichSuPhat VIEW/GPS theo MaThietBi
  DB --> HeartbeatController: viewed/visited ids + XP/level
  HeartbeatController --> MainPage: UserExperienceProfileResponse
  MainPage -> Preferences: MergeSavedPoiIds(viewed/visited)
  MainPage -> MainPage: UpdateCaiDatUI()
end

opt dong bo lich su local sau khi tai POI / vao lai man hinh
  MainPage -> DeviceIdentity: GetDeviceId()
  MainPage -> HeartbeatController: POST /api/heartbeat/sync-history
  HeartbeatController -> DB: kiem tra VIEW/GPS da co\nchen thieu tu ViewedPoiIds/VisitedPoiIds
  DB --> HeartbeatController: insertedViews / insertedVisits
  HeartbeatController --> MainPage: 200 OK
end

Guest -> MainPage: nhap SearchEntry
MainPage -> MainPage: OnSearchTextChanged()\nGetVisiblePois()\nRenderPoiCards()

Guest -> MainPage: bam "Xem chi tiet"
MainPage -> MainPage: OpenPoiDetailAsync(poi)\nRecordViewedPoi(poi)
MainPage -> Preferences: Save viewed_poi_ids
MainPage -> HeartbeatController: POST /api/heartbeat/view
HeartbeatController -> DB: dedup 5 phut + insert LichSuPhat(Nguon="VIEW")
DB --> HeartbeatController: saved
MainPage -> HeartbeatController: POST /api/heartbeat/sync-history
HeartbeatController -> DB: bo sung lich su local neu can
DB --> HeartbeatController: synced
MainPage -> MainPage: UpdateCaiDatUI()
MainPage -> DetailPage: PushAsync(new DetailPage(poi))

opt nguoi dung mo marker / sheet tren ban do
  Guest -> MainPage: bam marker POI
  MainPage -> MainPage: ShowMapPoiSheet(poi)\nnear badge / current selection
  Guest -> MainPage: bam "Xem chi tiet" tren sheet
  MainPage -> DetailPage: PushAsync(new DetailPage(poi))
end

alt nguoi dung copy ma thiet bi trong Cai dat
  Guest -> MainPage: OnCopyDeviceCodeClicked()
  MainPage -> DeviceIdentity: BuildRecoveryPayload()
  DeviceIdentity --> MainPage: payload
  MainPage -> Clipboard: SetTextAsync(payload)
else nguoi dung paste / nhap ma thiet bi
  Guest -> MainPage: OnPasteDeviceCodeClicked() / OnRestoreDeviceCodeClicked()
  MainPage -> MainPage: RestoreDeviceCodeAsync(code)
  MainPage -> DeviceIdentity: TrySetDeviceIdOverride(code)
  alt ma hop le
    DeviceIdentity --> MainPage: true
    MainPage -> AppConfig: EnsureApiBaseUrlAsync()
    MainPage -> DeviceIdentity: GetDeviceId()
    MainPage -> SubscriptionController: GET /api/subscription/status/{deviceId}
    SubscriptionController -> DB: doc DangKyApp theo ma thiet bi
    DB --> SubscriptionController: status
    SubscriptionController --> MainPage: CoDangKy, NgayHetHan,\nSoNgayConLai, LoaiGoi, DaDungThu
    MainPage -> Preferences: Set(da_dung_thu)\nSet(sub_ngay_het_han neu co)
    MainPage -> DeviceIdentity: GetDeviceId()
    MainPage -> HeartbeatController: GET /api/heartbeat/profile/{maThietBi}
    HeartbeatController -> DB: doc VIEW/GPS + XP/level
    DB --> HeartbeatController: profile
    HeartbeatController --> MainPage: UserExperienceProfileResponse
    MainPage -> HeartbeatController: POST /api/heartbeat/sync-history
    HeartbeatController -> DB: bo sung lich su local neu can
    DB --> HeartbeatController: synced
    MainPage -> MainPage: UpdateCaiDatUI()
    MainPage -> DeviceIdentity: BuildRecoveryPayload()
    DeviceIdentity --> MainPage: payload moi
    MainPage -> DeviceIdentity: BuildQrCodeUrl()
    DeviceIdentity --> MainPage: qrUrl moi
    MainPage -> Guest: DisplayAlert("Da khoi phuc")
  else ma khong hop le
    DeviceIdentity --> MainPage: false
    MainPage -> Guest: DisplayAlert("Ma khong hop le")
  end
else nguoi dung scan QR trong Cai dat
  Guest -> MainPage: OnScanDeviceQrClicked()
  MainPage -> MainPage: RequestAsync<Permissions.Camera>()
  alt duoc cap quyen camera
    MainPage -> QrScannerPage: PushModalAsync(new QrScannerPage(RestoreDeviceCodeAsync))
    QrScannerPage -> QrScannerPage: OnBarcodesDetected()
    QrScannerPage -> MainPage: RestoreDeviceCodeAsync(code)
    MainPage -> DeviceIdentity: TrySetDeviceIdOverride(code)
    alt ma hop le
      DeviceIdentity --> MainPage: true
      MainPage -> AppConfig: EnsureApiBaseUrlAsync()
      MainPage -> DeviceIdentity: GetDeviceId()
      MainPage -> SubscriptionController: GET /api/subscription/status/{deviceId}
      SubscriptionController -> DB: doc DangKyApp theo ma thiet bi
      DB --> SubscriptionController: status
      SubscriptionController --> MainPage: CoDangKy, NgayHetHan,\nSoNgayConLai, LoaiGoi, DaDungThu
      MainPage -> Preferences: Set(da_dung_thu)\nSet(sub_ngay_het_han neu co)
      MainPage -> DeviceIdentity: GetDeviceId()
      MainPage -> HeartbeatController: GET /api/heartbeat/profile/{maThietBi}
      HeartbeatController -> DB: doc VIEW/GPS + XP/level
      DB --> HeartbeatController: profile
      HeartbeatController --> MainPage: UserExperienceProfileResponse
      MainPage -> HeartbeatController: POST /api/heartbeat/sync-history
      HeartbeatController -> DB: bo sung lich su local neu can
      DB --> HeartbeatController: synced
      MainPage -> MainPage: UpdateCaiDatUI()
      MainPage -> DeviceIdentity: BuildRecoveryPayload()
      DeviceIdentity --> MainPage: payload moi
      MainPage -> DeviceIdentity: BuildQrCodeUrl()
      DeviceIdentity --> MainPage: qrUrl moi
      MainPage -> Guest: DisplayAlert("Da khoi phuc")
    else ma khong hop le
      DeviceIdentity --> MainPage: false
      MainPage -> Guest: DisplayAlert("Ma khong hop le")
    end
  else bi tu choi quyen camera
    MainPage -> Guest: hien thong bao can quyen camera
  end
end

opt refresh nen 20 giay
  MainPage -> AppConfig: EnsureApiBaseUrlAsync()
  MainPage -> PoiController: GET /api/poi
  alt API thanh cong
    PoiController -> DB: query lai POI
    DB --> PoiController: danh sach moi
    PoiController --> MainPage: List<PoiDto>
  else API loi
    PoiController --> MainPage: exception
    MainPage -> MainPage: giu _pois hien tai, bo qua refresh lan nay
  end
  MainPage -> MainPage: RefreshMapIfNeeded()
  alt POI signature thay doi
    MainPage -> MapWebView: rebuild map html va marker/circle
  else POI signature khong doi
    MainPage -> MapWebView: chi update user location
  end
  MainPage -> MainPage: RenderPoiCards()
end
@enduml
